
	Application Architecture (Logical Layers)
		> View
		> Controller
		> Service
		> Repository
		> Spring Data JPA
		> Hibernate Framework
		> JDBC Driver
		> Database
		
	Example
		> View
			- products.html
			- product_form.hmtl
		> Controller
			- ProductController
		> Service
			- ProductService
		> Repository
			- Product
			- ProductRepository